<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_348_r1l3"><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan> <expan>fr<ex>ewnde</ex></expan> als Jr vns <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> vnd <expan>gebette<ex>n</ex></expan> habt / <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<add><ab facs="#facs_348_r1l2"><expan>weıſh<ex>eit</ex></expan> </ab></add> <expan>ʒuu<ex>er</ex>ſchreıbe<ex>n</ex></expan> ob </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_348_r1l4">wır ıcht weſten wo vnſer <expan>gnedıgıſt<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> ~ der Römıſch etc künıg </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_348_r1l5">auf dıſʒ mal ʒufınden vnd was lewff in Beheim vnd von den </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_348_r1l6">Huſſen <expan>w<ex>er</ex>e</expan> etc . das haben wır wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> . Nu mag vns eẅr </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_348_r1l7"><expan>fürſıchtık<ex>eit</ex></expan> wol getrawen daʒ wır des wıllıg <expan>w<ex>er</ex>en</expan> ʒutun / ſo wıſſen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_348_r1l8">wır dıſʒ ʒeıt kein eygenſchaft wo <expan>derſ<ex>elb</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>gnedıgıſt<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> ~ der </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_348_r1l9">Römıſch etc kunıg <expan>yecʒ<ex>unden</ex></expan> ſey / ſo haben wır auch niht <expan>ſund<ex>er</ex>r</expan> <expan>treffenlıch<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_348_r1l10">meͣr von Beheim noch von den huſſen <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> ſeıd der ʒeıt daʒ <expan>vnſer<ex>r</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_348_r1l11"><expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> ~ der fürſten . eẅr <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> vnd <expan>and<ex>er</ex></expan> volk <expan>abgecʒog<ex>en</ex></expan> ſınd . Denn wo </ab>
